PLEASE READ.
I have never seen hatred amongst Indians and Pakistanis in the comment section related to music. There is so much love in this comment section between the two countries and it is absolutely mesmerizing. There is war amongst GOVERNMENTS. People are blind now. Imagine a world full of love, full of artists, musicians, sketchers, dancers and what not! Our world would be so much more beautiful. ART has never created war. This is art. The beauty of this song truly touches my soul. I strive to see more love  between the the two countries, between the people living. ❤️
